<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Css on 雨巷</title><link>https://rainto.top/tags/css/</link><description>Recent content in Css on 雨巷</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Aug 2025 22:09:00 -0700</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://rainto.top/tags/css/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>字体自适应宽度</title><link>https://rainto.top/posts/note/20250811%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E8%87%AA%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Aug 2025 22:09:00 -0700</pubDate><guid>https://rainto.top/posts/note/20250811%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E8%87%AA%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>最近逛css award发现一个挺有意思的方法实现字体自适应宽度,所以记录下。&lt;a href="https://whoisguilty.com/">whoisguilty&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>

&lt;div id="hl-0" class="hl">
